#!/usr/local/projects/routing/help/html_filter.pl
<h2 align=center>Help for the "Email" field of the "Patron" table</h2>
This field contains the e-mail address of the patron in
<div class=field_format>address@domain</div>
format.  Note that the system does not standardly send e-mail to patrons
but is currently included to make it easy to notify them with bulletins
like weather-based outages, etc.

